232
00:14:37,655 --> 00:14:42,263
his father, his
mother, but he couldn't

233
00:14:42,263 --> 00:14:45,166
{\an1}kill his little brother.

234
00:14:45,166 --> 00:14:48,304
{\an1}He killed every shred
of feeling in his heart

235
00:14:48,304 --> 00:14:50,073
in order to
slaughter his own kin

236
00:14:50,073 --> 00:14:54,179
{\an1}for the sake of his village.

237
00:14:54,179 --> 00:14:59,519
{\an1}But he just couldn't
bring himself to kill you.

238
00:14:59,519 --> 00:15:00,187
{\an1}Do you understand
what that means?

239
00:15:09,332 --> 00:15:12,736
{\an1}To him, your life was even
more precious than the village.

240
00:15:17,142 --> 00:15:20,380
{\an1}Until the moment of his death...
no, even after he died,

241
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:24,619
{\an1}it was all for you,
to confer on you new powers.

242
00:15:24,619 --> 00:15:29,024
{\an1}By allowing you to defeat him,
he had avenged the Uchiha clan.

243
00:15:29,024 --> 00:15:34,533
{\an1}He made you the hero of
the Hidden Leaf Village.

244
00:15:34,533 --> 00:15:38,670
{\an1}Ravaged by illness, painfully
aware of his impending death,

245
00:15:38,670 --> 00:15:43,211
{\an1}he forcefully prolonged his
life with medication, all

246
00:15:43,211 --> 00:15:44,646
{\an1}for the sake of his
beloved little brother.

247
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:52,824
{\an1}Because he had to fight you
and die in your presence.

248
00:16:03,104 --> 00:16:05,774
{\an1}For the peace of the
Hidden Leaf Village,

249
00:16:05,774 --> 00:16:09,613
{\an1}and most of all for
you, Sasuke Uchiha,

250
00:16:09,613 --> 00:16:14,119
{\an1}he wanted to die being known
as a criminal, and a traitor.

251
00:16:14,119 --> 00:16:16,923
{\an1}He accepted disgrace
in the place of honor,

252
00:16:16,923 --> 00:16:20,295
{\an1}and hatred in the place of love.

253
00:16:20,295 --> 00:16:25,234
{\an1}And yet, Itachi still died
with a smile on his face.

254
00:16:25,234 --> 00:16:28,338
He bequeathed to
you the Uchiha name,

255
00:16:28,338 --> 00:16:30,007
{\an1}still fooling you
to the very end.

256
00:16:39,386 --> 00:16:39,720
{\an1}ITACHI: I'm home!

257
00:16:43,758 --> 00:16:46,896
{\an1}-Welcome home, Itachi!

258
00:16:46,896 --> 00:16:49,367
Hey come on,
let's go outside play together.

259
00:16:49,367 --> 00:16:50,902
{\an1}So what do you think we
should go play first?

260
00:16:50,902 --> 00:16:53,339
{\an1}-Stop that, Sasuke.

261
00:16:53,339 --> 00:16:55,976
{\an1}Your brother has academy
homework to do first.

262
00:16:55,976 --> 00:16:58,312
{\an1}You could play after
he's finished doing that.

263
00:16:58,312 --> 00:16:58,713
SASUKE: But Mom!

264
00:17:03,486 --> 00:17:06,089
- It's OK,
I can do my homework later.

265
00:17:06,089 --> 00:17:07,558
{\an1}Besides, it's easy.

266
00:17:07,558 --> 00:17:11,664
-Oh, goodness.

267
00:17:11,664 --> 00:17:12,531
{\an1}SASUKE (THINKING): I wonder
where he could be hiding.

268
00:17:18,573 --> 00:17:19,707
-Ha!

269
00:17:19,707 --> 00:17:22,578
{\an1}I found you, big brother!

270
00:17:22,578 --> 00:17:24,714
{\an1}-You're pretty sharp, Sasuke.

271
00:17:24,714 --> 00:17:26,182
But too bad!

272
00:17:26,182 --> 00:17:27,050
-Aww!

273
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:29,521
{\an1}That's so not fair!

274
00:17:29,521 --> 00:17:30,922
Hey Dad?

275
00:17:30,922 --> 00:17:33,192
-Huh?

276
00:17:33,192 --> 00:17:35,194
{\an1}- Itachi and I were out
playing hide and seek today,

277
00:17:35,194 --> 00:17:37,565
{\an1}but then he used a clone jutsu
