278
00:17:37,565 --> 00:17:39,934
{\an1}And that's cheating, isn't it?

279
00:17:39,934 --> 00:17:44,675
{\an1}- Oh, you've mastered
using the clone jutsu?

280
00:17:44,675 --> 00:17:46,711
{\an1}- Hey wait, you could
teach me the clone jutsu

