{\an1}ITACHI: It'll have to wait.

289
00:18:05,402 --> 00:18:06,671
{\an1}I have an important
mission tomorrow.

290
00:18:06,671 --> 00:18:09,841
I must prepare.

291
00:18:09,841 --> 00:18:10,376
{\an1}SASUKE: You're such
a big fat liar.

292
00:18:18,587 --> 00:18:20,489
-Sorry, Sasuke.

293
00:18:20,489 --> 00:18:21,190
{\an1}Maybe some other time.

294
