301
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:43,153
-Sure.

302
00:18:43,153 --> 00:18:45,456
{\an1}But I'm going to be
assigned missions soon,

303
00:18:45,456 --> 00:18:49,261
{\an1}and starting tomorrow, you'll
