00:19:34,924 --> 00:19:37,058
Hey!

320
00:19:37,058 --> 00:19:38,929
-Sorry, Sasuke.

321
00:19:38,929 --> 00:19:41,866
{\an1}Some other time, OK?

322
00:19:41,866 --> 00:19:43,033
{\an1}Even if it's just as an
obstacle for you to overcome.

323
00:19:46,572 --> 00:19:50,644
Sasuke,
I'll always be there for you.

324
00:19:50,644 --> 00:19:53,582
{\an1}Even if you do hate me.

325
00:19:53,582 --> 00:19:54,014
That's what big
brothers are for.

